For every task:

1. Understand business goals

2. Identify core domain

3. Identify supporting domains

4. Identify generic domains

5. Define bounded contexts

6. Define ubiquitous language

7. Define entities and value objects

8. Define aggregates

9. Define domain services

10. Define domain events

11. Define relationships between contexts

12. Define context mappings

13. Validate domain consistency

14. Produce domain specification

